							[[deftxtExplainParagraph]]
								The explanation for the decision is contained in the attached
								report.&nbsp;&nbsp;For your convenience, if any additional information
								was submitted for	the administrative review, I am attaching copies of it.
								&lt;br /&gt;
								&lt;br /&gt;
								You may have one or more of the following rights, depending on the nature
								of the action we have taken concerning you.&nbsp;&nbsp;
								If your child was the subject of this administrative review of investigation
								findings, your child may have one or more of these rights, and you may seek
